    "description": "《矮人与地城》正式版终于和大家见面了！现有三名可用角色，四张地图及对应敌人和Boss，希望大家能够喜欢。游戏在三消的基础上进行创新，结合肉鸽游戏的要素，带来与众不同的全新体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/cb760ab2bc5cb810362ad262615ad0b5.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/282ae5bb14f8c1ac4fda6877908bc3b8.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/282ae5bb14f8c1ac4fda6877908bc3b8.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/282ae5bb14f8c1ac4fda6877908bc3b8.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在《矮人与地城》中，一切都离不开<strong>连线</strong>，无论是积蓄力量消灭敌人，还是稳固防御远离危险，亦或是拾取金币，为将来做打算，都需要通过连线完成。角色可以在长距离连线后获得经验值，提升等级并学习有益的技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/0a4b7f53bc08085258219d0d2ffee932.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/27ea4830a1952b15771d584d62e987e4.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/27ea4830a1952b15771d584d62e987e4.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/27ea4830a1952b15771d584d62e987e4.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏中共有三名可选角色：<strong>寻宝矮人</strong>、<strong>蒸汽猎人</strong>和<strong>深渊术士</strong>。他们拥有不同的机制、符文和战斗方式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/499c34b2d47ccfa5a8e2392c5bd089b1.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/b96056d9bf9e0c5d931843916ee41e69.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/b96056d9bf9e0c5d931843916ee41e69.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/b96056d9bf9e0c5d931843916ee41e69.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在战斗中获取并替换符文，调整构筑，发挥不同流派的特色。更高效地完成连线。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/59d7c9b5d915e23d937844a2ec25bfdf.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/c3d70a2e4cfecbaba9cccc0938ba237a.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/c3d70a2e4cfecbaba9cccc0938ba237a.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/c3d70a2e4cfecbaba9cccc0938ba237a.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>棋盘上会出现多种类型的随机事件，有些可以增强你的属性，有些则可以强化符文。但是要抓紧脚步，时间一到，它们就会消失不见。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/ad66358d963793485559d9f52fb951c3.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/3f350a0cd76f7f587116107b9bdd93f5.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/3f350a0cd76f7f587116107b9bdd93f5.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/3f350a0cd76f7f587116107b9bdd93f5.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>无论战斗胜利与否，所有收集的金币可用于建设营地，升级铁匠铺、在工坊制作卷轴、在小屋强化基础属性……活用营地中的各类设施，让冒险更加轻松。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >致敬</h2><strong>本游戏最初灵感来自于著名游戏：《Dungeon Raid》</strong>",
